Body:
Are they, then, not aware that they are being tested year-in,
			year-out?<span class='fn'>167</span> And yet, they do not repent and do not
			bethink themselves [of God];

Fight against them! God will chastise them by your hands, and
			will bring disgrace upon them, and will succour you against them;
			and He will soothe the bosoms of those who believe,
